{"body": "The prescribed weekly rates of the daily living component for the purposes of section 78(3) of the Act are- the standard rate, £76.70; and the enhanced rate, £114.60. The prescribed weekly rates of the mobility component for the purposes of section 79(3) of the Act are- the standard rate, £30.30; and the enhanced rate, £80.00.", "citation_label": "UKSI 2013/377 reg. 24", "citation_path": "uk/regulation/uksi/2013/377/24", "document_class": "regulation", "expression_date": "2026-04-06", "heading": "Rate of personal independence payment", "id": "60c4393b-58c2-5944-8b3a-a8d28020bbef", "identifiers": {"legislation.gov.uk:number": "377", "legislation.gov.uk:provision": "24", "legislation.gov.uk:type": "uksi", "legislation.gov.uk:year": "2013"}, "jurisdiction": "uk", "kind": "regulation", "language": "en", "legal_identifier": "UKSI 2013/377 reg. 24", "level": 1, "metadata": {"extent": ["E+W+S"], "references_to": ["ukpga/2012/5/78", "ukpga/2012/5/79", "uksi/2026/148/article/15", "ssi/2026/171/article/8"], "retrieved_at": "2026-06-05T07:35:00Z"}, "ordinal": 24, "parent_citation_path": "uk/regulation/uksi/2013/377", "parent_id": "8957f52a-ff78-55a7-a31b-7251d4aee6b6", "source_as_of": "2026-04-06", "source_document_id": "uksi/2013/377", "source_format": "legislation.gov.uk-clml", "source_id": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/377/regulation/24/2026-04-06", "source_path": "sources/uk/regulation/2026-06-05-uk-pip-reg24/uksi/2013/377/regulation-24.xml", "source_url": "https://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2013/377/regulation/24/2026-04-06", "version": "2026-06-05-uk-pip-reg24"}
